A4.text: Kaine was the junior United States senator from Virginia since 2013.

A5.text: After Senator Jim Webb's decision not to seek reelection, Kaine announced on April 5, 2011, that he would run for Webb's seat.

A6.text: Tim Kaine replaced Jim Webb as senator on January 3, 2013.

A7.text: Mark Warner became Virginia's senior senator in 2013.
